snippet.title: How I Optimize My Week For Increased Output (As A Programmer)
snippet.description:
How I Optimize My Week For Increased Output (As A Programmer)

"Clean Code Friday"
If you want to receive one short email from me every week, where I go through a few of the most useful things I have explored and discovered this week. Things like; favourite apps, articles, podcasts, books, coding tips and tricks. Then feel free to join https://kalletech.com/clean-code-friday/

AlgoExpert: https://www.algoexpert.io/kalle30

TrackAdvance
Apple app store: https://itunes.apple.com/se/app/trackadvance/id1464248884?l=en&mt=8

Google play store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kallehallden.trackahead

In this video I show you how I optimize my week in order to increase my output (or productivity).
I hope you enjoy it!
